{"tid":1603980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 抄《榮光》出醜 何君堯割席 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-09-29T23:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T19:32:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a39b42933b92a1f15bdaadaf08538faa99cb4f93","tid":1603980,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:36:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190930/20778131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F20778131&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0281118d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F20778131&h=b6a6f328\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190930/20778131</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n抄《榮光》出醜 何君堯割席 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190930/large/1569773749_8233.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190930%2Flarge%2F1569773749_8233.gif&h=b3b00fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何君堯個抄襲版MV下架，有網民幫佢po返配正版歌詞，笑佢「唱獨歌」。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前立法會議員何君堯同一班自稱「愛香港文化藝術工作者」，將《願榮光歸香港》改成撐警歌詞，自己仲親自領唱，結果首歌俾網民report侵權而喺YouTube下架，仲要俾網民恥笑藍絲冇腦，只識偷同抄人哋嘢，亦有人質疑何係「執葉律師」，冇理由唔知咁做係侵犯版權，算唔算知法犯法？<br />\n<br />\n搞出呢件醜事，連條片都冇埋，作為領唱好威威嘅何君堯就真係威，佢前晚喺facebook開直播，第一件事梗係光速割席，話成單嘢係「朋友」搞嘅，係有「朋友」認為要有個「光榮版」，之後就由「朋友」製作咗呢條片，又話唔清楚點係侵權，聲稱歌曲本身冇登記版權、作曲人身份冇確認，所以佢「朋友」拎嚟再填詞冇問題，只係二次創作。<br />\n<br />\n但YouTube喺下架解釋中，已講明條片含有Goomusic版權內容，且對方已因版權因素封鎖影片，而Goomusic正係由歌手何韻詩創立，屬獨立音樂品牌，即係唔係何君堯所講冇版權喎！不過何「執葉律師」亦戴晒頭盔，講明成單嘢唔關佢事，係佢「朋友」嘅事，有乜事就入佢「朋友」數啦，而佢本人就已飛去北京出席中共建政70年活動。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：萬人接機嚇窒？ 777兜深圳返港 (李八方)"},{"pid":"7c619d293306a4428b1eddd0fbcda42057e13a1b","tid":1603980,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:38:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">流氓假律師</span></span>"},{"pid":"81a08c7e9acd8f59273acfc7edf73051cb485133","tid":1603980,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:38:55.000Z","msg":"佢朋友咪 689，兩個都仆街黎"},{"pid":"e376ef68fb9582bd1481e107fff1c8312b0a261f","tid":1603980,"uid":41545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:44:56.000Z","msg":"唔係咁撚柒吓譁？<br />\n唱完都唔敢認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d15b41c1b93fdb52f3ceabdcea3b4b37d9212d","tid":1603980,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:49:21.000Z","msg":"嗰日見何妖榮光版一出，我就幫佢tag咗上人民日報個fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1560b8b99e9d70de17dea51e3cbb2baae6ffb944","tid":1603980,"uid":108571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:16:48.000Z","msg":"多謝hocc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eff3622c9786d59f57751889b77ff06305d43b2","tid":1603980,"uid":67325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:21:02.000Z","msg":"正柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a258733e5e6c68e024079c75cac26e59714edc","tid":1603980,"uid":130702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:21:42.000Z","msg":"見微博啲人話無拎嚟商業用途就可以改<br />\n話utube,fb一隻歌都唔畀播係美國封鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人真係無知識產權架呢樣野㗎啵<br />\n何妖仲將首願平安歸香港置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bccb5ddbbdfc0